{"tid":1765981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(暴徒) 施永青 曾參與「六七暴動」, 上街擲石, 自製炸彈, 追打警察, 只為「發洩」","createTime":"2019-12-02T09:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T05:44:38.000Z","uid":134071,"like":414,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"98e35473d2f22c278e085fc517b2f83cd4506b34","tid":1765981,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"施永青成日屌手足, 忍唔住起佢底<br />\n原來施永青曾參與「六七暴動」, 佢仲暗示自己有反社會人格 (話自己使用暴力, 並非為&quot;革命熱情&quot;, 而係為左發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20150805-hongkong-Sze/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20150805-hongkong-Sze%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0fDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=5e7cfbfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20150805-hongkong-Sze/</a><br />\n<br />\n一生與共 施永青<br />\n<br />\n在共產主義仍是反叛標誌的年代，少年施永青迷上共產，後來成為富商，為神功或為子弟，他依然一生與共。<br />\n特約撰稿人 陳勝藍 發自香港<br />\n2015-09-05<br />\n.....<br />\n1967年左派反英暴動，這個左仔上街擲石、派單張，並將烽煙帶進校園。為了宣示對黃姓校長不滿，用香燭炮仗自製計時炸彈，放在天台，算準放學時間香燭燒盡，引爆炮仗，炸斷卷着直幡的草繩，同學們聞聲抬頭，但見「打倒黃老闆」5大字。<br />\n<br />\n以下圖片, 來自賣港01 (唔駛貼link, 睇cap圖就夠)<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/qST3ebB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqST3ebB.jpg&h=b8b066b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09b65adc5f6a2f00c2f762b90eb78c3b9302de1f","tid":1765981,"uid":134071,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"仆街, 呢班土共暴徒發洩, 害死唔少平民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac8ebf3bf5ddb892feea14672c544cb256964b2","tid":1765981,"uid":53003,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:08:18.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"194b8d3c28925ac7ac7a56af775cbf618153379e","tid":1765981,"uid":96,"like":141,"dislike":1,"score":140,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"淨係改人聖誕卡都知佢咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5752f9a56db9cc998549df805c996894f868580e","tid":1765981,"uid":335434,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"唔怪得呢排咁燥 原來係恨鐵不成鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160154e072c9819373465b42deea83216733eba5","tid":1765981,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"194b8d3c28925ac7ac7a56af775cbf618153379e","tid":1765981,"uid":96,"like":141,"dislike":1,"score":140,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"淨係改人聖誕卡都知佢咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995aae7267c13e92ffc35b66074ce7ec513de31d","tid":1765981,"uid":33473,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"佢好似講過<br />\n同長毛啊另外果d年輕果時信左翼<br />\n後來大左覺醒對左翼幻想破滅<br />\n咪信自由市場右翼"},{"pid":"6675118d8c05a27832a79d45142a18efda2fd788","tid":1765981,"uid":133806,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"Merry Christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e62e0338b6c5dec7e8a9529127605e58afa76e","tid":1765981,"uid":235025,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"918e7f918f6355362984c42f8389b73de0484533","tid":1765981,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"